          "title": "NEWBORN BABY IS RUMORED TO BE TWITTER'S NEXT CEO",
          "summary": "Twitter staff are speculating that Steve Davis, CEO of The Boring Company, could replace Elon Musk as the chief executive of Twitter. Davis' involvement in the recent layoffs at Twitter has caused employees to question his potential new role. He was asked to find ways to cut approximately $500 million in operating costs and ended up cutting $1 billion by terminating some contracts and negotiating others down. Davis and Musk have worked together since 2003.",
